---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Header />

  <main class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">About SNIST</h1>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-9">
          <img
            src="https://www.sreenidhi.edu.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/logo-snist.jpg"
            alt="Springer Logo"
            class="h-10 w-15 mx-auto mb-4"
          />
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-center">
            Journal Information
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <p>
              <strong>Establishment & Affiliation:</strong> Founded in 1997 by Sree
              Educational Society; affiliated with JNTU Hyderabad.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Accreditation:</strong> AICTE-approved, NBA-accredited.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Research & Development:</strong> Recognized for PhD programs
              and industrial research by DSIR.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Campus & Facilities:</strong> State-of-the-art labs, Wi-Fi,
              libraries, auditoriums, hostels, ATMs, and transport services.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Student Life:</strong> 30+ clubs for socio-cultural, academic,
              and extracurricular activities.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Placements:</strong> Strong track record with top corporate
              recruitments.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Notable Features:</strong> Focus on quality education, hands-on
              learning, and holistic student development.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">About Springer</h3>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <!-- <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Aims & Scope</h2> -->
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Springer is one of the world's leading scientific publishers,
            pioneering the future of publishing since 1842. Springer publishes
            high-quality peer-reviewed journals, books, and conference
            proceedings across a wide range of academic disciplines. With a
            global presence in over 20 countries and more than 8,000 employees
            worldwide, Springer publishes around 2,900 journals and 12,000 new
            books each year, and has the world's largest eBook collection in
            science, technology, and medicine. Springer's mission is to advance
            discovery by publishing robust and insightful research, supporting
            the development of new areas of knowledge, and making ideas and
            information accessible around the world. Visit Springer's Official
            Website
          </p>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">About ICNSIET</h3>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <!-- <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Author Guidelines</h2> -->
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-12">The Conference</h3>
            <p>
              The Department of Computer Science & Engineering, SNIST, proudly
              announces the International Conference on Neural Nexus and Synergy
              - Information in Emerging Technologies (ICNSIET) 2025. This
              prestigious event aims to bring together researchers,
              academicians, industry experts, and scholars from around the world
              to explore advancements in Neural Computing, Artificial
              Intelligence, and Emerging Technologies. ICNSIET 2025 serves as a
              dynamic platform for knowledge exchange, fostering discussions on
              groundbreaking developments across interdisciplinary domains. The
              conference seeks to drive innovation and establish a roadmap for
              future research in Computer Science & Engineering. The primary
              objective of ICNSIET 2025 is to enhance collaboration among
              researchers and professionals, facilitating the exchange of novel
              ideas, insights, and research breakthroughs that will shape the
              future of computing technologies. Participants will gain exposure
              to state-of-the-art advancements in AI-driven solutions, quantum
              computing paradigms, and digital ecosystems, revolutionizing
              industries worldwide. Additionally, ICNSIET 2025 aims to bridge
              the gap between academia and industry by inviting leading
              technology firms, startups, and industrialists to share their
              experiences, challenges, and success stories in implementing
              cutting-edge computational technologies in real-world
              applications.
            </p>
            <!-- <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
              <li>Manuscripts should be written in English</li>
              <li>Maximum length: 8000 words including references</li>
              <li>Abstract: 200-300 words</li>
              <li>Keywords: 4-6 keywords</li>
              <li>Format: IEEE conference format</li>
              <li>References: IEEE citation style</li> -->
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Review Policy</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
            <p>
              All submissions undergo a rigorous double-blind peer review
              process:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
              <li>Initial screening by editorial board</li>
              <li>Double-blind review by at least two expert reviewers</li>
              <li>Editorial decision based on reviewer recommendations</li>
              <li>Average review time: 4-6 weeks</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Plagiarism Policy</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
            <p>ICNSIET maintains a strict plagiarism policy:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
              <li>
                All submissions are checked using plagiarism detection software
              </li>
              <li>Maximum similarity index allowed: 15%</li>
              <li>Zero tolerance for plagiarism and self-plagiarism</li>
              <li>Authors must properly cite all sources</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Submission Details</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
            <p>To submit your paper:</p>
            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
              <li>Register on our submission portal</li>
              <li>Follow the submission template</li>
              <li>Submit all required documents and forms</li>
              <li>Track your submission status online</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="mt-6">
              <a
                href="/submit"
                class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors"
              >
                Submit Your Paper
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
